title: Zeitmonds Are Fortrender 7/30: Michael Che, Billie Eilish, Prince, US Fencing Team, Mike Lindell, Emma Stone, House of Gucci
itunes:title: Zeitmonds Are Fortrender 7/30: Michael Che, Billie Eilish, Prince, US Fencing Team, Mike Lindell, Emma Stone, House of Gucci
description:
In this edition of Zeitmonds Are Fortrender, Miles and Super Producer Anna Hossnieh discuss Michel Che getting dragged for jokes about Simone Biles, Billie Eilish's new album, Prince's first posthumous album release, US Fencers wearing pink masks after teammate is accused of sexual assault, Mike Lindell pulling 'My Pillow' ads from Fox News, Emma Stone hopping on the 'sue Disney' train, and the trailer for 'House of Gucci'
